        "subject": "LU-14950 osc: No page transfer get/put for DIO",
        "message": "LU-14950 osc: No page transfer get/put for DIO\n\nPage transfer get/put is not required for DIO pages, which\nare guaranteed to have other references.\n\nThe get/put for this takes a little over 4% of the CPU time\nin DIO, so it's worthwhile to remove it for DIO pages.\n\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <pfarrell@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I82ecc989df4b12687a0f4744ffa6367988b3e65c\n"
